author: SkinnyTaste
name: Zucchini Casserole

ingredients.notes: squeezed dry with a towel after

ingredients.ingred_name: kosher salt and fresh black pepper

instructions: Preheat oven to 350°F. Mix everything together in a bowl. Spray 9 x 13-inch baking dish with cooking spray and pour mixture. Bake until golden brown and a toothpick inserted in the center comes out clean, approximately 45 to 50 minutes. Cut into 12 equal pieces.
